{
  "stem": "935.5",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was the middle of summer, middle of August.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Incredibly hot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "No water.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And too crowded, everything, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Nobody knew where or what.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They-- they put the cartons with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was a separate wagon for Erdman, for the big shots-- also separate from all the others.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My group, of course, we had-- I had practiced escape, practiced from beam to beam under the thing, and all of it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This cattle car ride, which now everybody who knows about Auschwitz knows about, or knows about cattle car drive, has been talked about and written about a million times-- can't even be-- come close to be described.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "First of all, now you're fenced in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Now there is that little bit of a window.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Like a monkey in a zoo, looking out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it is in one minute, so hot, that even the most prudish-- they have to undress.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You can't help it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We have to undress.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Of course, no facilities at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There's a bucket.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We had a women sitting on the bucket from the first moment on, all dressed in black.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I had never seen her before, I have no idea who she was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "She was like a character out of a Strindberg play.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You know, somebody who'd forgotten her lines, but was still wearing costume.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And she sat there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "She sat there all through it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And any time somebody needed to use the bucket, she would get up, turn her back, and the moment that was finished, she would sit again.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "She would not-- only her hands were moving all the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Somebody said that she had a son, a young son, in another wagon, who wanted to jump.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And she didn't want to see him get killed, so she had chosen-- chosen this wagon.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
